§wf:beautiful_mention v1.0
;; MINIMAL EXAMPLE — for learning purposes only.
;; See workflows/beautiful_mention.nodus for the full production-ready version.
;; This file demonstrates the basic NODUS workflow structure in ~10 lines.

@ON: new_mention
@steps:
1. ANALYZE($in.text) ~sentiment → $s
2. ?IF $s > 0.8 → GEN(thank_you) → $out
